"title": "5409: metaphor",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5409: metaphor",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An image which suggests similarities between two different ideas, without implying that they are identical. Scripture uses metaphors extensively, as a way of illustrating aspects of its teaching.</p>\n<h2>Examples of metaphors for God</h2>\n<h3>Father</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:6\">DEU 32:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:8\">ISA 64:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:10\">MAL 2:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:6\">EPH 4:6</a></p>\n<h3>Rock</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:4\">DEU 32:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:2\">1SA 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:2\">2SA 22:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:2\">PSA 62:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:35\">PSA 78:35</a></p>\n<h3>Shepherd</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:1\">PSA 23:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:9\">PSA 28:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:1\">PSA 80:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:11-Ezek34:16\">EZK 34:11–34:16</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of metaphors for Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Bread of life</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:35-John6:51\">JHN 6:35–6:51</a></p>\n<h3>Good shepherd</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:11\">JHN 10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:14\">JHN 10:14</a></p>\n<h3>Light of the world</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:12\">JHN 8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:5\">JHN 9:5</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of metaphors for the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<h3>Counsellor</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16\">JHN 14:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:7\">JHN 16:7</a></p>\n<h3>Breath</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:7\">GEN 2:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job32:8\">JOB 32:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:4\">JOB 33:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:14\">JOB 34:14</a></p>\n<h3>Wind</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:8\">JHN 3:8</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of metaphors for the church</h2>\n<h3>Bride</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:7\">REV 19:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:2-Rev21:9\">REV 21:2–21:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:17\">REV 22:17</a></p>\n<h3>Household of God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:19\">EPH 2:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:15\">1TI 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>Body of Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:4\">ROM 12:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:12-1Cor12:27\">1CO 12:12–12:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:22-Eph1:23\">EPH 1:22–1:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:24\">COL 1:24</a></p>",
